{
  "stem": "268.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the new guy looks at me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, I thought you're saving a Polish national.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You're saving a damn Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he use very bad language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, can't you see he's a Jew?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I say, who?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told you I speak street Polish, with some cuss words and something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I dig into my lexicon to whatever I could find to really-- and so he says, no, he's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So there's this new guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He says, well, he doesn't talk like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that doesn't mean he's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He says, listen, he says, you want to pull his pants down?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And by this time, I knew the truth will come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I, out of desperation, I said, you know, who gave you the right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You're the only one that's going to survive here by yourself?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The war is over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And tomorrow we could be liberated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you're telling me I'm not Polish because I'm Jewish because you're going to pull my pants down?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I really-- whatever I said, I put some cuss words in it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, you know, you talk smart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll give you a break at daytime.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by evening-- this was in the morning-- by evening, if you're still here, I'll bring the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, so this place better be empty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So naturally, I was grateful that he gave me at least a chance to get away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I got up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew this was too dangerous to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I start marching.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came to the next village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to actually go through another town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the roads were blocked by then and Luftwaffe was shooting up to some aircraft.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
